title: Total Exports of Cotton Piece Goods for Great Britain
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1851-1921 (2)--Original Data, 1921-1936. Irish Free State Excluded After April 1, 1923. No Mention Is Made Of "Flags, Handkerchiefs And Shawls" Beginning 1933. However, The Data For 1932, Excluding These Items Are As Follows: January - 180; February - 180; March - 203; April - 199; May - 201; June - 185; July - 198; August - 181, September - 177; October - 138; November - 159; December - 196. Source: Accounts Relating To Trade And Navigation

This NBER data series m07036b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 7 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter07.html.
